        <Parent_String>grapples [300426703], pincers [300024743], holding and gripping tools [300024735], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
